---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Resume"
  description="Resume for Adam Lacroix Sneed: Senior Solutions Architect specializing in PAM, identity engineering, and agentic AI systems."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl space-y-10">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start justify-between gap-4">
      <div class="space-y-2">
        <p class="eyebrow">Resume</p>
        <h1 class="section-title">Adam Lacroix Sneed</h1>
        <p class="text-textMuted flex flex-wrap gap-x-3 gap-y-1">
          <span>Austin, TX</span>
          <span class="text-borderTone">¬∑</span>
          <a href="mailto:adam@adamsneed.com" class="transition hover:text-accent">adam@adamsneed.com</a>
          <span class="text-borderTone">¬∑</span>
          <a href="https://adamsneed.com" class="transition hover:text-accent">adamsneed.com</a>
          <span class="text-borderTone">¬∑</span>
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/adam-sneed-8113375/" class="transition hover:text-accent">LinkedIn</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn-primary" href="/resume/adam-sneed-resume.pdf" download>
        Download PDF
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Summary -->
    <div class="card border-l-4 border-l-accent/60" data-reveal>
      <p class="text-textMain leading-relaxed">
        Senior Solutions Architect and PAM subject matter expert with deep expertise in identity &amp; access management
        and agentic AI systems. 20+ years in IT with 4+ years focused on enterprise PAM/EPM and IAM solutions.
        Designs and deploys secure, scalable automation ‚Äî from credential vaulting, identity lifecycle management,
        and session governance to AI-driven workflow orchestration with human-in-the-loop guardrails.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Technical Skills -->
    <div class="space-y-4" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">Technical Skills</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {[
          'PAM/EPM Architecture', 'IAM & Identity Governance', 'Credential Vaulting & Rotation',
          'Identity Lifecycle', 'SIEM/SOAR & ITSM', 'Zero Trust', 'Cloud IAM (AWS/Azure/GCP)',
          'AD/Entra ID', 'PowerShell', 'Python', 'SQL', 'REST APIs', 'Terraform & Ansible',
          'CI/CD Pipelines', 'Agentic Workflow Design', 'Prompt Engineering',
          'AI-Assisted Automation', 'Multi-Agent Systems', 'Agent Orchestration',
          'Policy Enforcement', 'NIST/CIS/ISO 27001', 'SOX/PCI', 'Agile (Scrum/Kanban)'
        ].map((skill) => (
          <span class="rounded-full border border-borderTone/60 bg-panel/50 px-3 py-1 text-sm text-textMuted">{skill}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Experience -->
    <div class="space-y-6" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">Professional Experience</h2>

      <!-- Netwrix -->
      <div class="card space-y-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-textMain">Netwrix Corporation</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-textMuted">Remote from Austin, TX</p>
          </div>
          <span class="rounded-full border border-accent/30 bg-accentSoft px-3 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold text-accent">Current</span>
        </div>
        <p class="font-medium text-textMain">Senior Solutions Architect, Privileged Access Management <span class="font-normal text-textMuted">¬∑ Sep 2021 ‚Äì Present</span></p>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-textMuted leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>PAM subject matter expert for enterprise deployments across Fortune-class organizations ‚Äî credential vaulting, session proxying, JIT access, and service account governance integrated with AD/Entra ID, AWS/Azure cloud IAM, SIEM/SOAR, and ITSM platforms.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>Architect API-driven automation frameworks (PowerShell, Python, REST APIs) for privileged account lifecycle management ‚Äî onboarding, credential rotation, access workflows ‚Äî enforcing least-privilege policies at scale.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>Design operational runbooks, decision-logic SOPs, and escalation policies that translate directly to agentic workflow patterns ‚Äî conditional branching, retry logic, human-in-the-loop approval gates, and automated remediation.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>Lead root cause analysis and platform resilience engineering; build reusable knowledge bases ensuring operational continuity across teams.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>Oversee vendor-led PAM implementations including SOW scoping, UAT, and production cutovers within Agile delivery frameworks.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <!-- Award callout -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 rounded-lg border border-accent/20 bg-accentSoft/50 px-4 py-3">
          <span class="text-2xl">üèÜ</span>
          <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-textMain">Netwrix Hero Award</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-textMuted">Q1 FY'25 ‚Äî Excellence in enterprise PAM solution delivery</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Agentic -->
      <div class="card space-y-4 border-l-4 border-l-accent/40">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-textMain">Agentic &amp; AI Systems Engineering</h3>
          <span class="text-sm text-textMuted">2024 ‚Äì Present</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-textMuted leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>Design, build, and operate a production multi-agent system ‚Äî 5+ specialized AI agents coordinating across security monitoring, business intelligence, home automation, and infrastructure management with defined roles, guardrails, and chain-of-command policies.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>Engineer prompt-driven workflows with structured output parsing, verification loops, retry logic, approval gates, and failure handling ‚Äî reliability engineering applied to AI automation.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>Build AI-driven business intelligence pipelines: automated competitor monitoring, web scraping, LLM-powered analysis, and branded email digest delivery.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
