            <span>Security-first agent architecture: credential isolation, tool-use policies, output sanitization, injection detection, and mandatory code scanning before execution.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>Cross-agent communication protocols, session orchestration, and workflow engines with webhook triggers, template variables, and status-driven state machines.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- GCS -->
      <div class="card space-y-4">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-baseline justify-between gap-2">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-textMain">GCS Technologies</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-textMuted">Austin, TX</p>
