          <span class="text-sm text-textMuted">2012 ‚Äì 2021</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="rounded-full border border-borderTone/50 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs text-textMuted">Director of Operations</span>
          <span class="rounded-full border border-borderTone/50 px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs text-textMuted">Technical Support Manager</span>
