        <ul class="space-y-2.5 text-textMuted leading-relaxed">
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>Progressed from datacenter operations to directing a business unit ‚Äî P&amp;L ownership, strategic initiatives, and a 30-member team while exceeding revenue targets for seven consecutive quarters.</span>
