            <span>Built training programs that increased team utilization from 73% to 86%; designed customer feedback loops that measurably improved retention.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex gap-2">
            <span class="mt-2 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-accent/60"></span>
            <span>Led cross-functional security initiatives aligning IAM practices with compliance requirements and business objectives.</span>
